		<title>玩耍也有學問！與狗狗互動前該知道的這5件事</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/13/%e7%8e%a9%e8%80%8d%e4%b9%9f%e6%9c%89%e5%ad%b8%e5%95%8f%ef%bc%81%e8%88%87%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%ba%92%e5%8b%95%e5%89%8d%e8%a9%b2%e7%9f%a5%e9%81%93%e7%9a%84%e9%80%995%e4%bb%b6%e4%ba%8b/</link>
		
